John D. NAGLE, as Commissioner of Immigration for the Port of San Francisco, Appellant, v. YIP TONG SHUN, Appellee. No. 6092. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. March 31, 1930.

Before DIETRICH and WILBUR, Circuit Judges, and NORCROSS, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to motion of counsel for the appellant the appeal herein is dismissed; mandate forthwith.
